# Meris LLM — pick ONE provider block below (see: meris models list)
# Copy to .env in repo root or your project cwd.
#
# 重要：
# - 每次运行只用「一家」厂商 + 一个 model（由 MERIS_PROVIDER 或 settings.json models 路由决定）
# - 下面各段是「备选模板」，请只取消注释你要用的那一段，不要同时填多家 Key
# - 各厂商主 Key 变量名不同（DEEPSEEK_* / OPENAI_* / DASHSCOPE_* …），不会互相覆盖
# - 冲突来自：未设 MERIS_PROVIDER 时填了多个 Key，或 MERIS_BASE_URL 与 MERIS_PROVIDER 不一致
# - 任务路由（models.byMode）时可在 .env 保留多家 Key，由 settings 指定用谁
# - base_url / model：有配置用配置，无配置用 preset 内置默认
#   · 全局: MERIS_BASE_URL / MERIS_MODEL（仅作用于当前解析到的 provider）
#   · 分厂商: DEEPSEEK_BASE_URL、ARK_BASE_URL、VOLCENGINE_BASE_URL、DEEPSEEK_MODEL 等
#
# 验证：meris models list · meris doctor

# --- DeepSeek ---
# MERIS_PROVIDER=deepseek
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=
# MERIS_MODEL=deepseek-chat

# --- OpenAI ---
# MERIS_PROVIDER=openai
# OPENAI_API_KEY=

# --- Anthropic (pip install meris-agent[anthropic]) ---
# MERIS_PROVIDER=anthropic
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# --- Google Gemini (OpenAI-compatible endpoint) ---
# MERIS_PROVIDER=gemini
# GEMINI_API_KEY=

# --- 智谱 GLM ---
# MERIS_PROVIDER=glm
# ZHIPU_API_KEY=

# --- Moonshot / Kimi ---
# MERIS_PROVIDER=moonshot
# MOONSHOT_API_KEY=

# --- 阿里通义 / 百炼 (DashScope OpenAI 兼容) ---
# MERIS_PROVIDER=qwen
# DASHSCOPE_API_KEY=
# MERIS_MODEL=qwen-plus

# --- 火山引擎 方舟 / 豆包 ---
# MERIS_PROVIDER=volcengine
# ARK_API_KEY=
# MERIS_MODEL=ep-xxxxxxxx
# ARK_BASE_URL=https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3

# --- 自部署 vLLM / Xinference / LiteLLM ---
# MERIS_PROVIDER=local
# MERIS_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000/v1
# MERIS_MODEL=your-model
# OPENAI_API_KEY=not-needed

# --- Groq / Mistral / OpenRouter ---
# MERIS_PROVIDER=groq
# GROQ_API_KEY=
# MERIS_PROVIDER=mistral
# MISTRAL_API_KEY=
# MERIS_PROVIDER=openrouter
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=

# --- Ollama (local, no key required) ---
# MERIS_PROVIDER=ollama
# MERIS_MODEL=llama3.2

# Override preset defaults (any provider):
# MERIS_BASE_URL=https://api.deepseek.com/v1
# MERIS_MODEL=deepseek-chat

# Legacy 通用名（可选，多家 preset 的「后备」Key，易与专用 Key 混淆 — 建议优先用上面的专用变量）
# LLM_API_KEY=
# LLM_BASE_URL=
# LLM_MODEL=
# LLM_PROVIDER=

# Optional: meris-rs context compression
# MERIS_NATIVE=1
